genresAdvancedInfo.name: rock paraibano
genresAdvancedInfo.description: This genre of rock music originates from the state of Paraiba, Brazil. It has a distinct sound that blends elements of traditional Brazilian music with rock and roll. The lyrics often touch on themes of social justice and political activism, reflecting the state's history of political struggle. Bands like Seu Pereira e Coletivo 401 and Cabruêra are popular representatives of this genre.
